it has 'a09'.\n\nSo correctLastOR would NOT be found (no OR gate has 'z01' as an input).\n\nThe issue: when AND(x_maxBit, y_maxBit)'s output is ALSO swapped, its new output name doesn't appear in the OR gate's inputs. The OR gate still references the old wire name.\n\nPlease confirm this analysis and describe what the correct approach should be to handle this case - where the last-bit generate AND's output is itself swapped, so we can't find the correct OR gate by following the (now-swapped) output of the AND gate."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01AbtRdKdptG1ykPhBsvVqQF","session_id":"3718bd19-0ddf-4b76-8212-0c47cbec5f2b","uuid":"f5c60d84-d4a9-45f6-80a5-fb3fd5479681"}
